WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:44.000
[Episode 12]

01:50.000 --> 01:51.000
Hello, Mr. Ji.

01:51.620 --> 01:52.070
Hello.

01:52.070 --> 01:52.870
Hello, Mr. Ji.

01:54.560 --> 01:56.640
Yin Xiang, let Ms. Xu come here.

01:56.640 --> 01:58.000
Okay, I'll go get her.

02:01.360 --> 02:02.160
Jia.

02:04.180 --> 02:05.140
Luo Qingping.

02:06.380 --> 02:07.300
Ke Wenxue.

02:20.870 --> 02:22.650
It's your working time now.

02:22.680 --> 02:24.510
Do the room attendants of Purong Hotel

02:24.510 --> 02:25.960
like to chat while working?

02:25.960 --> 02:27.120
I just wanted to provide guests

02:27.120 --> 02:28.870
- with more attentive service.
- Then, do you know

02:28.870 --> 02:30.910
what the first principle of service is?

02:30.910 --> 02:32.310
It is not to disturb your guests.

02:32.310 --> 02:34.190
Could you go to any room

02:34.500 --> 02:35.760
on the executive floor

02:35.800 --> 02:37.750
and get me a bottle of shampoo?

02:37.800 --> 02:39.280
I know what you've discovered.

02:39.280 --> 02:41.340
But it is not the time to report it yet.

02:41.510 --> 02:42.390
I'm right here.

02:42.829 --> 02:43.810
Always?

02:43.980 --> 02:45.110
I'll always be here.

02:45.680 --> 02:46.560
Miyu.

02:47.870 --> 02:48.630
Miyu.

02:53.710 --> 02:55.190
What's more,
I noticed your hair accessories.

02:55.190 --> 02:56.520
They should be uniform.

02:56.590 --> 02:57.430
Understood?

02:59.380 --> 03:00.220
Ms. Xu.

03:00.370 --> 03:02.160
Mr. Ji.

03:02.600 --> 03:04.000
How is the check-in situation today?

03:04.000 --> 03:05.190
Two check-ins

03:05.190 --> 03:06.310
and three check-outs.

03:06.310 --> 03:08.760
How did you handle the linens
in these rooms?

03:08.760 --> 03:10.670
We used freshly laundered linens
from the new factory

03:10.670 --> 03:12.390
and informed the guests.

03:12.410 --> 03:13.130
Good.

03:14.170 --> 03:16.050
No matter how many guests we have,

03:16.200 --> 03:18.040
our service must not slack off.

03:18.370 --> 03:19.810
Now, go back to your posts

03:19.980 --> 03:21.420
and do your jobs well.

03:21.650 --> 03:22.370
Dismissed.

03:22.600 --> 03:23.440
Okay.

03:27.350 --> 03:29.200
You are the backbone
of the executive floor.

03:29.200 --> 03:30.510
Before the guests have left,

03:30.510 --> 03:32.040
don't fall apart yourself.

03:42.070 --> 03:43.100
Room service.

03:45.450 --> 03:47.550
Hello, I am the forewoman
of the executive floor.

03:47.550 --> 03:49.440
May I help you?

03:49.910 --> 03:51.410
Close the door and come in.

03:52.210 --> 03:54.010
Whatever it is, just say it here.

03:57.140 --> 03:58.900
You are Xu Miyu,

03:59.020 --> 04:00.820
the one trending online, right?

04:00.830 --> 04:03.630
I wonder who you're taking the blame for.

04:07.030 --> 04:07.270
[Xu Kai, Journalist]

04:07.100 --> 04:08.030
Don't be afraid.

04:08.240 --> 04:09.300
[Xu Kai, Journalist]

04:08.280 --> 04:09.280
I am a journalist.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.800
I know the corrupt upper management

04:11.800 --> 04:13.830
will definitely use you,
lower-level staff, as scapegoats.

04:13.830 --> 04:14.590
Speak up.

04:14.630 --> 04:16.630
We in the media can speak out for you.

04:17.320 --> 04:19.589
Sorry, you misunderstood.

04:22.870 --> 04:24.040
You don't admit it

04:24.360 --> 04:26.150
because you're afraid of
getting into trouble, right?

04:26.150 --> 04:28.030
But you should know that
once this is exposed,

04:28.030 --> 04:29.470
no one can stay out of it.

04:29.490 --> 04:30.920
Just standing here, you are a story.

04:30.920 --> 04:31.600
Do you know that?

04:31.600 --> 04:32.630
I have no story.

04:33.630 --> 04:35.310
Please don't make one up.

04:37.870 --> 04:38.390
Do you know

04:38.390 --> 04:39.800
your silence means

04:39.800 --> 04:41.310
you are covering and indulging

04:41.310 --> 04:42.390
for illegal discipline?

04:42.390 --> 04:44.560
Because of people like you,
who refuse to report what you know,

04:44.560 --> 04:45.720
upholding justice

04:45.720 --> 04:47.190
becomes even harder.

04:47.240 --> 04:48.900
Are you trying to frighten me?

04:52.750 --> 04:55.810
You must be Mr. Ji,
the new general manager here, right?

04:56.510 --> 04:58.970
Perfect. Let's sync up
on some information.

05:02.880 --> 05:04.680
Which media outlet are you from?

05:06.800 --> 05:07.670
Me?

05:07.900 --> 05:09.070
I am a freelancer.

05:09.070 --> 05:10.480
If all media were like you,

05:10.480 --> 05:12.120
the courts would be flooded
with subpoenas.

05:12.120 --> 05:14.360
You've already constituted a provocation.

05:14.360 --> 05:16.690
I can call the police
on behalf of the hotel

05:17.350 --> 05:19.750
and have your social media account banned.

05:29.410 --> 05:31.240
Ms. Xu. Ms. Xu.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.800
Mr. Feng wants you in his office.

05:32.800 --> 05:33.630
Copy that.

05:34.360 --> 05:35.820
Mr. Feng is looking for me.

05:35.950 --> 05:37.510
I'm afraid someone has already
made up a story about

05:37.510 --> 05:38.500
what happened to you

05:38.500 --> 05:40.060
and told Feng Kaixin.

05:41.159 --> 05:42.159
Go.

05:42.550 --> 05:44.159
You can only prove yourself
by going there.

05:44.159 --> 05:45.010
Okay.

05:53.650 --> 05:59.060
[Purong Hotel]

05:53.790 --> 05:55.920
I heard a reporter
interviewed you just now.

05:55.920 --> 05:56.920
What did you say to him?

05:56.920 --> 05:57.870
I didn't say anything.

05:57.870 --> 05:59.120
Don't pretend with me.

05:59.120 --> 06:00.750
So many people in the HSKP Department
saw it.

06:00.750 --> 06:01.950
How could I wrong you?

06:03.630 --> 06:04.870
Because of the detergent incident,

06:04.870 --> 06:06.510
I've already been very controversial.

06:06.510 --> 06:08.110
I know the power of the media.

06:08.150 --> 06:09.070
In this situation,

06:09.070 --> 06:10.120
if I talk nonsense,

06:10.120 --> 06:11.920
wouldn't I be asking for trouble?

06:11.920 --> 06:13.120
You talk a good game.

06:13.510 --> 06:14.190
But who knows what bad intentions

06:14.190 --> 06:15.360
you have in mind?

06:16.360 --> 06:17.070
Follow me.

06:17.130 --> 06:18.250
We're going to see Mr. Wei.

06:18.250 --> 06:19.290
Why?

06:19.580 --> 06:20.610
You know the reason.

06:20.610 --> 06:21.820
It's because of what you did.

06:21.820 --> 06:22.630
Go.

06:23.020 --> 06:26.000
[Director's Office]

06:23.240 --> 06:25.040
Let's see what you say to Mr. Wei.

06:25.560 --> 06:27.220
- Stop pretending.
- Mr. Feng.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.120
Mr. Ji.

06:31.480 --> 06:33.480
Mr. Ji, what brings you here?

06:34.560 --> 06:35.560
Ms. Xu is here too.

06:35.470 --> 06:38.510
[Director's Office]

06:36.130 --> 06:38.870
Yes, I was just about to report to you.

06:39.250 --> 06:39.750
She

06:39.950 --> 06:42.440
communicated privately with reporters
living on the executive floor.

06:42.440 --> 06:43.960
It is very unfavorable for us

06:43.960 --> 06:45.390
to carry out crisis public relations.

06:45.390 --> 06:47.159
When Ms. Xu was being pestered,

06:47.180 --> 06:48.180
I saw everything.

06:49.780 --> 06:51.360
She didn't say a single word
to that journalist

06:51.360 --> 06:52.430
that would harm

06:52.430 --> 06:55.030
the reputation and interests of
Purong Hotel.

06:55.360 --> 06:57.550
Ms. Xu was
deceived by the actual perpetrator,

06:57.550 --> 06:59.790
just like us.

07:00.310 --> 07:02.350
She's just a scapegoat.

07:04.200 --> 07:05.890
What do you say, Mr. Feng?

07:07.400 --> 07:08.750
What a big mistake!

07:09.430 --> 07:10.570
You have been wronged.

07:10.570 --> 07:11.690
I care so much

07:11.720 --> 07:12.990
about Purong Hotel

07:13.010 --> 07:15.300
that I was too stressed out from working.

07:15.400 --> 07:16.460
Please forgive me.

07:17.870 --> 07:18.680
Mr. Ji,

07:19.120 --> 07:20.240
do you have

07:20.240 --> 07:21.560
anything else to tell me?

07:21.560 --> 07:23.360
Or are you here just for Ms. Xu?

07:23.800 --> 07:26.070
I came here to remind you of
the meeting later.

07:26.070 --> 07:27.800
I hope you will be there on time.

07:28.960 --> 07:30.830
Don't dare to bother you.

07:30.870 --> 07:32.000
I was just about to go.

07:32.000 --> 07:32.870
Shall we go?

07:33.180 --> 07:35.530
[Director's Office]

07:34.180 --> 07:34.750
Ms. Xu,

07:34.980 --> 07:35.840
go do your work.

07:44.860 --> 07:46.470
After you, Mr. Feng.

07:46.860 --> 07:48.010
After you.

07:54.680 --> 07:55.190
Excuse me.

07:55.190 --> 07:56.510
Hurry up! Make way.

08:04.330 --> 08:05.050
Mr. Feng.

08:08.770 --> 08:09.580
Take a look.

08:19.950 --> 08:21.210
[Total Bacteria: exceeding the limit]
[E. Coli: exceeding the limit]

08:25.570 --> 08:25.990
Mr. Wei.

08:25.660 --> 08:26.160
[Purong Hotel]

08:26.010 --> 08:27.340
- Mr. Wei.
- Mr. Wei.

08:26.180 --> 08:26.670
[Pujiang River Flows with Eternal Glory,
as Purong Hotel Accompanies You]

08:27.360 --> 08:27.950
Mr. Wei.

08:31.460 --> 08:33.990
[Purong Hotel]

08:37.000 --> 08:37.840
Sit.

08:37.780 --> 08:39.059
[Purong Hotel]

08:46.430 --> 08:48.380
Mr. Wei, shall we start?

08:48.810 --> 08:49.690
Yes.

08:49.730 --> 08:50.660
No need to ask me.

08:51.280 --> 08:53.000
Some of you may not know yet.

08:53.000 --> 08:53.960
Let me introduce.

08:53.960 --> 08:56.250
This gentleman sitting in my seat is

08:56.270 --> 08:57.270
Ji Feng.

08:56.330 --> 08:57.990
[Purong Hotel]

08:57.550 --> 08:58.550
He is

08:58.020 --> 08:59.370
[Pujiang River Flows with Eternal Glory,
as Purong Hotel Accompanies You]

08:58.550 --> 09:00.630
the new general manager of Purong Hotel.

09:00.630 --> 09:02.430
Let's applaud to welcome Mr. Ji.

09:10.240 --> 09:12.930
[Purong Hotel]

09:12.350 --> 09:13.550
Thank you, everyone.

09:13.890 --> 09:15.510
It's my first time meeting you all

09:15.510 --> 09:17.750
and we run into such an emergency.

09:18.270 --> 09:19.930
It is indeed a bit unexpected.

09:20.550 --> 09:21.860
But the incident has already happened.

09:21.860 --> 09:23.130
We just have to face it.

09:24.360 --> 09:25.240
Mr. Feng,

09:26.120 --> 09:28.920
how does the HSKP Department
plan to handle it now?

09:30.200 --> 09:31.520
Here's the situation, Mr. Ji.

09:31.520 --> 09:32.610
As for the outsourced laundry factory,

09:32.610 --> 09:35.150
we terminated the contract
with it immediately.

09:35.150 --> 09:37.510
Now we have switched
to a new laundry factory,

09:37.510 --> 09:39.360
called Weimin Laundry Factory.

09:39.790 --> 09:40.960
Is it your way of

09:40.960 --> 09:42.160
solving the problem?

09:44.660 --> 09:45.800
The hotel linens

09:46.320 --> 09:47.960
have had excessive bleach for years.

09:47.960 --> 09:49.750
Is it simply a washing problem?

09:51.500 --> 09:53.110
Excessive bleach

09:53.170 --> 09:54.500
is the laundry's fault…

09:54.510 --> 09:56.360
How does the hotel supervise

09:56.360 --> 09:57.560
the laundry process?

09:57.710 --> 09:58.980
How often are the linens cleaned?

09:58.980 --> 10:00.250
What are the cleaning standards?

10:00.250 --> 10:02.220
Are there regular spot checks
by testing agencies?

10:02.220 --> 10:03.120
Mr. Feng, can you

10:03.120 --> 10:04.180
explain this to us?

10:05.540 --> 10:07.320
Well, I'm sorry.

10:07.320 --> 10:09.580
I have to go back and check the materials.

10:09.870 --> 10:12.210
This is not about checking materials.

10:12.230 --> 10:15.360
It's about the poor supervision of
the HSKP Department.

10:15.830 --> 10:16.960
From top to bottom,

10:17.670 --> 10:19.740
you turn a blind eye to inferior products.

10:19.740 --> 10:20.930
When problems occur,

10:20.930 --> 10:23.400
you let the bottom-level attendants
take the blame.

10:23.400 --> 10:25.030
Is this what the HSKP Department of

10:25.030 --> 10:26.630
a five-star hotel should do?

10:27.310 --> 10:28.330
What we need to solve

10:28.330 --> 10:30.450
is not just the problem of the laundry.

10:30.450 --> 10:32.440
The whole linen supply chain of
the HSKP Department

10:32.440 --> 10:33.680
should be changed.

10:35.800 --> 10:37.840
I don't think that's necessary.

10:37.870 --> 10:40.190
Excessive bleach

10:40.240 --> 10:42.240
is only a laundry compliance issue.

10:42.240 --> 10:43.810
There's nothing wrong with the linens.

10:43.810 --> 10:45.240
The fact that there's no problem
with the linens

10:45.240 --> 10:47.370
doesn't mean the linens are flawless.

10:48.290 --> 10:49.440
Our bedding

10:49.730 --> 10:52.750
does not meet the standards
of a luxury hotel in itself.

10:52.750 --> 10:53.750
The guests on the executive floor

10:53.750 --> 10:55.320
are like‌ burnt children dread the fire.

10:55.320 --> 10:57.470
You don't want to get caught again, right?

10:57.470 --> 10:58.240
No.

10:59.760 --> 11:00.860
I mean,

11:01.240 --> 11:03.100
changing the bedding supplier is

11:03.100 --> 11:05.050
a big deal.

11:05.480 --> 11:07.170
From product selection to trial,

11:07.170 --> 11:09.260
it will take at least two to three weeks.

11:09.260 --> 11:10.400
Not only does it waste money and manpower,

11:10.400 --> 11:12.560
but it can't solve an urgent problem.

11:12.600 --> 11:14.310
So you want to walk around it
when a big deal comes,

11:14.310 --> 11:15.070
right?

11:15.290 --> 11:16.560
Then, our concepts are really

11:16.560 --> 11:17.400
different.

11:18.030 --> 11:19.720
Mr. Feng believes in muddling along,

11:19.720 --> 11:22.580
while I prefer resolving the issue
once and for all.

11:24.830 --> 11:25.910
Everyone here is

11:25.910 --> 11:28.240
a management elite
in the hotel industry.

11:28.250 --> 11:29.670
Please use your resources

11:29.670 --> 11:31.790
to find a new bedding supplier.

11:32.050 --> 11:33.760
The quantity, price, and standard

11:33.760 --> 11:35.960
have been sent to your corporate email.

11:36.120 --> 11:38.750
Managers of each department
should collect all the proposals

11:38.750 --> 11:41.880
and submit them to my office
by the end of business today.

11:42.180 --> 11:43.310
Meeting adjourned.

11:56.050 --> 11:57.740
Mr. Wei asks you to take the initiative

11:57.740 --> 11:58.830
and make amends.

12:24.410 --> 12:25.320
You guys go first.

12:25.320 --> 12:26.380
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

12:44.510 --> 12:46.310
About the linen supplier issue,

12:46.370 --> 12:49.320
don't expect too much
from the subordinates.

12:49.630 --> 12:51.870
They are just here for a free ride.

12:51.900 --> 12:54.140
You need to understand your situation.

12:54.460 --> 12:55.360
You are anxious,

12:55.360 --> 12:56.480
but they are not in a hurry at all.

12:56.480 --> 12:57.270
I know.

12:57.870 --> 13:00.340
So I can take this opportunity to
see who is working

13:00.340 --> 13:01.310
and who is slacking off.

13:01.310 --> 13:03.710
Ji Feng, do you have that much time?

13:03.920 --> 13:06.480
Feng Kaixin was right at the meeting.

13:06.510 --> 13:07.970
If there's a major change,

13:08.160 --> 13:10.240
the transition period

13:10.260 --> 13:11.570
will be very painful.

13:11.670 --> 13:12.400
Don't worry.

13:13.030 --> 13:14.510
I've already contacted a laundry.

13:14.510 --> 13:15.810
We'll work with them
for three months first.

13:15.810 --> 13:17.030
We can change if it doesn't work out.

13:17.030 --> 13:19.250
I've also found backup suppliers.

13:19.270 --> 13:20.100
So fast?

13:21.030 --> 13:22.980
I cooperated with them
when I was at Siwei.

13:22.980 --> 13:24.040
We are old friends.

13:24.960 --> 13:27.560
They will ship the goods
at this time tomorrow.

13:30.130 --> 13:30.890
Wait.

13:32.060 --> 13:34.030
Where did you get the money from?

13:34.600 --> 13:36.920
I haven't heard anything
in the finance department.

13:36.920 --> 13:39.190
That's the general manager's
emergency fund

13:39.190 --> 13:40.400
especially approved by the board.

13:40.400 --> 13:41.800
No one knows about it yet.

13:43.310 --> 13:44.820
Pretend to advance along one path

13:44.820 --> 13:46.700
while secretly attacking another.

13:46.700 --> 13:47.720
To break the monopoly

13:47.720 --> 13:48.890
and test

13:48.920 --> 13:50.650
where there will be a response.

13:51.100 --> 13:51.890
Awesome.

13:52.350 --> 13:53.280
I'm leaving now.

14:01.720 --> 14:03.160
Okay, this cart is ready too.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.110
Go ahead.

14:06.990 --> 14:08.400
In just a few days,

14:09.030 --> 14:12.090
things have completely changed.

14:12.770 --> 14:14.910
Yesterday, we were still repeatedly
changing these linens,

14:14.910 --> 14:17.170
and today they all have to be cleared out.

14:17.960 --> 14:18.960
It's so deserted.

14:19.890 --> 14:21.690
Out with the old, in with the new.

14:21.710 --> 14:23.310
What's so good about the new?

14:23.440 --> 14:24.630
Let me tell you, if the new ones are good,

14:24.630 --> 14:25.840
they're harder to serve.

14:25.840 --> 14:26.550
Ms. Xu.

14:26.580 --> 14:28.820
Have the linens on the executive floor
been packed yet?

14:28.820 --> 14:29.360
Done.

14:29.360 --> 14:31.160
The last cart is coming right up.

14:38.550 --> 14:40.530
Do you think Miyu knew about it?

14:41.030 --> 14:41.960
Knew about what?

14:42.350 --> 14:45.430
About Mr. Ji becoming the general manager.

14:45.460 --> 14:47.440
Think about it. If she knew,

14:47.750 --> 14:50.010
could she be an undercover sent by Mr. Ji?

14:50.050 --> 14:52.410
Madam Cailu got into trouble

14:52.440 --> 14:53.460
and Drunkard Feng got bad luck,

14:53.460 --> 14:54.870
while she became the forewoman.

14:54.870 --> 14:56.530
Doesn't it all make sense now?

14:57.360 --> 14:59.550
Could she be the big boss
behind the scenes?

14:59.550 --> 15:00.550
Big boss?

15:02.270 --> 15:04.320
If she were the big boss,

15:04.870 --> 15:07.150
would Drunkard Feng be able to
bully her like that?

15:07.150 --> 15:09.080
Drunkard Feng and Mr. Wei

15:09.080 --> 15:10.750
are in the same boat.

15:11.030 --> 15:13.030
But Mr. Ji pushed out Mr. Wei.

15:13.390 --> 15:14.590
Doesn't it all add up?

15:14.790 --> 15:17.150
If you put it that way,

15:18.010 --> 15:20.520
she's the general manager's favorite.

15:21.410 --> 15:22.530
If that's the case,

15:22.560 --> 15:24.450
couldn't she even
get a little overtime pay?

15:24.450 --> 15:26.250
Do you believe she didn't get it?

15:26.390 --> 15:28.750
Maybe she pocketed it all.

15:30.700 --> 15:33.030
Miyu isn't that kind of person.

15:37.030 --> 15:38.980
[HSKP Department Management Work Group]

15:40.000 --> 15:42.750
Notice to all managers, supervisors,
forewomen, and foremen.

15:42.750 --> 15:45.350
We are now collecting information
on linen suppliers.

15:45.350 --> 15:47.460
Please fill out the proposal template

15:47.460 --> 15:50.620
and submit it to the HSKP Department
corporate email by the end of the day.

15:50.620 --> 15:52.630
Have you finished tidying up
the linens on your floor?

15:52.630 --> 15:53.750
Just finished.

15:54.300 --> 15:55.630
Did you see the message in the group?

15:55.630 --> 15:58.000
I did, but it has nothing to do with us.

15:58.020 --> 15:59.500
How could we

15:59.530 --> 16:02.040
have any channels for linen suppliers?

16:02.150 --> 16:04.440
Feng's notices are getting
more and more ridiculous.

16:04.440 --> 16:06.220
He dares to make any kind of request.

16:06.220 --> 16:07.410
Just ignore him. I guess

16:07.410 --> 16:09.480
he's rushing to flatter the new boss.

16:09.500 --> 16:11.220
So, he just said it,

16:11.250 --> 16:13.070
and we just forget it.

16:20.320 --> 16:22.630
[Purong Hotel]

16:28.870 --> 16:29.630
Ms. Xu.

16:31.180 --> 16:32.440
I thought you weren't here.

16:32.440 --> 16:34.240
I saw you hung the cleaning sign.

16:35.390 --> 16:37.270
I intended to go out.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.920
Just tidy up a bit.

16:38.950 --> 16:39.710
Okay.

16:40.110 --> 16:40.960
By the way.

16:41.680 --> 16:43.240
Thank you

16:43.570 --> 16:45.810
for helping me out with that reporter,

16:47.000 --> 16:49.000
and for the media exchange meeting.

16:49.120 --> 16:50.250
Thank you very much.

16:53.750 --> 16:56.150
I just hope you can
pull yourself together.

16:57.150 --> 16:59.030
We are in the same boat now.

16:59.390 --> 17:01.790
If you don't want Purong Hotel to

17:01.790 --> 17:02.920
decline gradually,

17:03.030 --> 17:05.000
we have to pull together.

17:05.260 --> 17:06.020
Understand?

17:10.010 --> 17:10.940
Get back to work.

17:11.460 --> 17:12.060
Okay.

17:17.109 --> 17:17.960
Hi, Martri.

17:21.170 --> 17:21.890
What?

17:22.640 --> 17:24.530
The goods are stuck at customs?

17:25.740 --> 17:26.770
Come on.

17:27.369 --> 17:28.329
Martri,

17:28.720 --> 17:29.920
I'm serious.

17:32.800 --> 17:34.600
How long will it be held on?

17:36.050 --> 17:39.250
Oh, please try something out
with the customs officials.

17:39.280 --> 17:40.570
I need a final date

17:40.590 --> 17:43.590
and announce it at the press conference

17:43.620 --> 17:45.220
tomorrow.

17:45.920 --> 17:46.890
Okay.

17:54.450 --> 17:55.810
Is Mr. Liu there?

17:58.130 --> 18:00.520
I'll go find him right away.

17:58.910 --> 18:00.280
[Purong Hotel]

18:00.550 --> 18:02.000
Please let him know.

18:14.510 --> 18:15.240
Hello.

18:15.400 --> 18:16.480
Asilan,

18:16.480 --> 18:17.630
can you hear me?

18:17.960 --> 18:21.240
I can't hear you clearly.
Please wait a moment.

18:23.720 --> 18:24.400
Hello.

18:25.070 --> 18:26.790
The machines inside are too loud.

18:26.790 --> 18:27.960
Ms. Xu.

18:27.960 --> 18:30.200
Are the guesthouse beddings
working out well?

18:30.200 --> 18:31.750
Do you need to restock?

18:31.750 --> 18:33.640
They're great.
I'm not restocking this time.

18:33.640 --> 18:34.970
I'm placing a new order.

18:35.000 --> 18:36.030
How many?

18:36.480 --> 18:37.720
2,000 sets of

18:37.720 --> 18:39.830
13-piece bedding set,
including slippers.

18:39.830 --> 18:41.000
Can you supply that?

18:41.000 --> 18:42.160
That's a lot.

18:42.310 --> 18:44.700
Your guesthouse business must be booming.

18:44.700 --> 18:45.880
It's not for the guesthouse this time.

18:45.880 --> 18:47.640
It's for a five-star hotel.

18:47.640 --> 18:50.030
If you can keep the high-quality,

18:50.050 --> 18:51.840
we'll order even more.

18:51.860 --> 18:52.750
Aslan,

18:52.780 --> 18:53.750
can you hurry up

18:53.750 --> 18:55.160
to send me a sample?

18:55.160 --> 18:56.550
How soon can it arrive?

18:56.550 --> 18:58.880
Tomorrow. It'll arrive tomorrow.

18:58.880 --> 19:00.280
I'll expedite it for you.

19:00.450 --> 19:01.440
Don't forget to send me

19:01.440 --> 19:02.920
your product qualification certificates.

19:02.920 --> 19:04.440
Okay, I'll send them right away.

19:04.440 --> 19:05.070
Goodbye.

19:05.070 --> 19:06.480
Okay, that's it. Bye.

19:07.410 --> 19:07.850
[Aslan]

19:07.870 --> 19:08.490
[Yunhai Cotton Mill, Brand Introduction]

19:10.350 --> 19:11.740
[Test Report]

19:20.890 --> 19:24.540
[Director's Office]

19:25.590 --> 19:27.050
Ms. Xu, what's the matter?

19:27.350 --> 19:30.030
I'm here to submit the proposal
for the linen supplier.

19:30.030 --> 19:31.170
Just leave it to me.

19:31.890 --> 19:34.040
Can I hand it to Mr. Feng myself?

19:34.070 --> 19:35.200
There are some details

19:35.200 --> 19:37.200
that I want to explain to him in person.

19:37.200 --> 19:38.440
Mr. Feng is with a client right now.

19:38.440 --> 19:39.570
He's not available.

19:39.640 --> 19:43.100
Okay, please pass it on to him for me.

19:42.720 --> 19:44.840
[Director's Office]

19:43.240 --> 19:45.240
Thank you for your hard work, Ms. Xu.

19:47.270 --> 19:50.980
[Director's Office]

19:55.920 --> 19:59.230
[Director's Office]

20:02.740 --> 20:03.370
Mr. Li.

20:03.770 --> 20:04.770
This price cut is

20:04.790 --> 20:06.230
just for show.

20:06.590 --> 20:08.750
We'll make the proposal look good to

20:08.830 --> 20:10.360
secure the contract first.

20:10.440 --> 20:11.410
Next time,

20:11.440 --> 20:13.440
we'll raise the price back.

20:13.460 --> 20:14.310
Okay?

20:17.500 --> 20:18.020
Yes.

20:21.090 --> 20:22.970
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

20:22.990 --> 20:24.580
[Proposer: Xu Miyu]

20:30.630 --> 20:31.530
Yes. Yes.

20:34.090 --> 20:34.370
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

20:34.500 --> 20:37.260
[Supplier Introduction]

20:37.400 --> 20:37.670
[Cooperation Plan]

20:43.550 --> 20:45.590
For our long-lasting cooperation,

20:46.820 --> 20:47.740
my treat tonight, okay?

20:47.740 --> 20:49.070
We can talk while we eat.

20:49.620 --> 20:50.420
Okay.

20:55.030 --> 20:56.890
Book a private room
at Yuhuating Restaurant for me tonight.

20:56.890 --> 20:58.640
Mr. Feng, as for that proposal...

20:58.640 --> 20:59.990
Keep it here.

21:00.600 --> 21:01.750
Don't let Ji see it.

21:01.790 --> 21:03.450
Then, this deal won't be done.

21:04.480 --> 21:06.210
Dare she try to compete with me?

21:09.060 --> 21:13.810
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

21:31.370 --> 21:34.910
[Purong Hotel]

21:36.240 --> 21:39.220
[Purong Hotel]

21:47.670 --> 21:48.670
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

21:48.720 --> 21:49.810
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

21:49.890 --> 21:50.530
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

21:50.740 --> 21:51.250
[Xianglong Bedding Cotton Mill
Bedding Supply Plan]

22:00.270 --> 22:01.510
Just one proposal?

22:01.830 --> 22:03.160
From yesterday to today,

22:03.160 --> 22:04.790
only Mr. Feng from the HSKP Department

22:04.790 --> 22:06.510
submitted a proposal.

22:07.510 --> 22:09.280
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

22:09.280 --> 22:10.090
No problem.

22:18.230 --> 22:22.040
[General Manager's Office]

22:26.640 --> 22:27.470
Come in.

22:35.750 --> 22:36.440
Mr. Wei.

22:36.690 --> 22:39.040
Mr. Feng from the HSKP Department
has submitted the proposal.

22:39.040 --> 22:39.970
Here is a copy.

22:41.480 --> 22:42.660
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

22:42.730 --> 22:44.440
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

22:48.470 --> 22:49.670
Okay, go ahead.

23:02.460 --> 23:03.350
Mr. Feng.

23:03.620 --> 23:04.430
Mr. Qian.

23:04.540 --> 23:09.710
[Do not block the door.
Violators will receive a written warning]

23:14.750 --> 23:16.880
Bro, we have a deal.

23:16.900 --> 23:19.380
I'll be the only one
submitting the proposal.

23:19.380 --> 23:21.140
I will let Ji have no choice.

23:21.880 --> 23:23.840
Let's make sure we don't fight
amongst ourselves.

23:23.840 --> 23:26.640
Don't worry. I've already
made the arrangements.

23:27.680 --> 23:29.340
I can always count on you, bro.

23:31.440 --> 23:32.680
But

23:33.110 --> 23:35.590
why hasn't Ji come to me?

23:36.030 --> 23:37.010
Does he have

23:37.320 --> 23:39.270
other proposals?

23:40.400 --> 23:42.200
He's new to the job.

23:42.440 --> 23:44.480
He needs to save face.

23:44.720 --> 23:46.090
Stay calm.

23:46.960 --> 23:48.880
He's the one who needs you.

23:49.110 --> 23:50.680
You don't need him.

23:57.020 --> 23:57.840
I'm leaving.

24:08.030 --> 24:10.230
Any news from the customs negotiation?

24:11.410 --> 24:12.550
Why is it taking so long?

24:12.550 --> 24:13.950
We can't wait any longer.

24:14.720 --> 24:16.410
I need an answer as soon as possible.

24:16.410 --> 24:18.310
[Purong Hotel]

24:17.170 --> 24:18.640
Is Mr. Tao back?

24:19.720 --> 24:21.110
At the court? Which court?

24:20.530 --> 24:23.520
[Purong Hotel]

24:22.550 --> 24:23.790
Please contact him for me.

24:23.790 --> 24:25.250
I'll head there right now.

24:26.140 --> 24:27.770
[To Xu Miyu] [From Aslan]

24:29.710 --> 24:30.430
Thank you.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.240
Secretary Wu.

24:39.680 --> 24:41.610
We're off work. Mr. Wei isn't here,

24:41.720 --> 24:43.070
and neither is Mr. Ji.

24:43.130 --> 24:44.400
I'm not looking for them.

24:44.400 --> 24:45.760
I just want to ask you a question.

24:45.760 --> 24:46.830
Did you receive

24:46.830 --> 24:48.200
the bedding supplier proposals

24:48.200 --> 24:49.930
for the HSKP Department today?

24:50.450 --> 24:51.540
Why do you ask?

24:51.570 --> 24:52.910
I delivered a proposal.

24:53.000 --> 24:55.310
It has color pictures of the cotton fields

24:55.310 --> 24:56.200
in the northwest.

24:56.200 --> 24:57.590
I have no idea.

24:57.590 --> 24:59.130
When the general manager arrives tomorrow,

24:59.130 --> 25:00.530
you can ask him yourself.

25:01.900 --> 25:04.100
Sorry to keep you from getting off work.

25:30.200 --> 25:31.270
Hello, Mr. Tao.

25:31.270 --> 25:33.160
Yes, I just arrived at the hotel.

25:33.640 --> 25:35.900
I'll send the contract to you right away.

25:39.900 --> 25:42.490
Add another hundred yuan for each set?

25:43.940 --> 25:44.790
But Mr. Tao,

25:45.070 --> 25:47.710
we just agreed on the price an hour ago.

25:51.920 --> 25:54.160
Okay, let me think about it.

26:18.670 --> 26:19.310
Mr. Ji.

26:19.480 --> 26:21.400
I saw you weren't here just now,

26:21.400 --> 26:23.130
so I changed the bedding first.

26:23.180 --> 26:24.440
I was waiting for you to come back.

26:24.440 --> 26:26.310
I didn't ask for new bedding.

26:26.770 --> 26:29.110
This is a sample from the factory.

26:29.110 --> 26:30.960
I wanted to show it to you

26:30.960 --> 26:31.900
before the new product launch.

26:31.900 --> 26:34.110
But your schedule is fully booked,

26:34.110 --> 26:35.550
so I could only...

26:42.210 --> 26:43.310
[Washing instructions]

26:42.630 --> 26:44.030
Where is this brand from?

26:44.110 --> 26:46.200
Yunhai is a cotton processing plant

26:46.200 --> 26:47.400
in the Northwest region.

26:47.400 --> 26:49.250
They also produce their own cotton,

26:49.250 --> 26:51.000
as well as towels,

26:51.000 --> 26:52.260
bedding, and clothes.

26:52.350 --> 26:54.070
What about the specific parameters?

26:54.070 --> 26:55.830
The average fiber length of the cotton

26:55.830 --> 26:58.230
produced by their plant is 38 millimeters.

26:58.830 --> 27:00.590
The fineness is 9000 metric count.

27:00.590 --> 27:03.590
The single fiber strength
is around 4.9 cN.

27:05.110 --> 27:07.110
Do you have the product test report?

27:07.120 --> 27:09.920
I have the electronic version.
Please take a look.

27:11.390 --> 27:12.710
[Test Report]

27:12.650 --> 27:14.480
I've inspected many

27:12.740 --> 27:13.580
[Shanghai Institute of Quality Inspection
and Technical Research]

27:13.610 --> 27:14.510
[Test Report]

27:14.480 --> 27:16.070
cotton manufacturers in the Northwest.

27:15.890 --> 27:19.150
[Summary of Test Results
for Banned Azo Dyes]

27:16.720 --> 27:19.310
I think this one is
the most cost-effective.

27:19.550 --> 27:20.880
I also have some videos.

27:20.880 --> 27:21.740
Let me show you.

27:22.020 --> 27:22.590
Let me see.

27:22.060 --> 27:23.700
[Test Report]

27:33.440 --> 27:34.630
There's more if you swipe.

27:34.630 --> 27:35.990
[March 12, 2024]

27:36.300 --> 27:40.250
[March 12, 2024]

27:44.270 --> 27:45.590
They also showed me

27:45.590 --> 27:47.320
their cotton production base.

27:59.270 --> 28:00.880
These are the videos I took

28:00.880 --> 28:02.080
during my field trip.

28:04.510 --> 28:05.920
Why did you go there?

28:06.680 --> 28:08.790
My parents run a guesthouse back home.

28:08.790 --> 28:10.550
I helped them purchase some furniture,

28:10.550 --> 28:11.440
and linens.

28:11.550 --> 28:13.440
Yunhai was the manufacturer I picked.

28:13.440 --> 28:15.570
I felt that everything from logistics

28:15.590 --> 28:18.510
to the after-sales experience was great.

28:18.510 --> 28:20.350
This time I asked them to
send some samples,

28:20.350 --> 28:22.790
and they expedited the delivery
without hesitation.

28:22.790 --> 28:23.650
This is the set.

28:24.160 --> 28:25.480
Besides all-season duvet inserts,

28:25.480 --> 28:27.160
Purong Hotel usually uses summer
and winter duvet inserts

28:27.160 --> 28:28.680
according to the seasons.

28:28.680 --> 28:30.640
Have you taken this into consideration?

28:30.640 --> 28:32.100
Then, the pillow inserts.

28:32.750 --> 28:35.110
Guests with neck problems
need firm pillows.

28:35.110 --> 28:36.440
In the past, Purong Hotel

28:36.440 --> 28:38.830
always kept both
soft and firm ones in stock.

28:38.830 --> 28:39.640
Then, we have to think about the quantity.

28:39.640 --> 28:41.830
We have 368 rooms in total.

28:42.240 --> 28:43.160
We need at least three times the amount.

28:43.160 --> 28:45.110
That's over 1,100 sets in total

28:45.110 --> 28:46.350
to keep things running.

28:46.350 --> 28:48.270
Can they meet this supply volume?

28:49.160 --> 28:50.160
I wrote all of this

28:50.160 --> 28:51.590
in the report I submitted.

28:51.590 --> 28:52.680
Didn't you see it?

28:59.920 --> 29:01.320
You should have noticed.

29:01.440 --> 29:02.800
For this linen plan,

29:02.920 --> 29:04.680
the whole hotel is making way
for Feng Kaixin.

29:04.680 --> 29:06.920
They want to show me who the true boss is.

29:08.110 --> 29:09.200
You're so proactive.

29:09.200 --> 29:10.890
Aren't you afraid that he'll target you?

29:10.890 --> 29:12.510
They can't fire me

29:12.510 --> 29:14.040
because I work hard, right?

29:14.160 --> 29:15.960
And you said

29:15.980 --> 29:17.710
we must work together as a team.

29:19.030 --> 29:20.630
Send me that proposal again.

29:20.630 --> 29:22.550
Sure, I'll send it to you when I get back.

29:22.550 --> 29:24.000
Let me change the linen for you first

29:24.000 --> 29:26.240
because the sample hasn't been washed.

29:26.240 --> 29:26.790
It's okay.

29:26.790 --> 29:28.590
No need to get a new one, just use my set.

29:28.450 --> 29:30.460
♪ Life is full of ♪

29:31.240 --> 29:33.930
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

29:35.600 --> 29:39.360
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

29:40.550 --> 29:41.620
Hold this for me first.

29:41.030 --> 29:43.030
♪ All those confusions ♪

29:43.630 --> 29:47.350
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

29:48.230 --> 29:52.230
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

29:52.090 --> 29:53.090
Give it to me.

29:53.570 --> 29:54.330
Come on.

29:55.630 --> 29:58.040
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

29:59.160 --> 30:01.080
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

30:02.560 --> 30:06.560
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

30:08.430 --> 30:10.360
♪ Busy and restless ♪

30:10.830 --> 30:14.260
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

30:15.580 --> 30:19.750
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

30:17.810 --> 30:19.610
What are you looking at? Help me.

30:21.670 --> 30:24.130
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

30:25.350 --> 30:27.320
♪ Don't look back ♪

30:28.350 --> 30:30.080
♪ I've already learned ♪

30:30.900 --> 30:34.610
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

30:35.420 --> 30:36.990
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

30:37.950 --> 30:41.860
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

30:42.810 --> 30:45.550
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

30:46.440 --> 30:48.760
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

30:47.920 --> 30:48.680
Come on.

30:49.670 --> 30:51.310
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

30:50.830 --> 30:51.550
Okay.

31:03.360 --> 31:05.820
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

31:07.040 --> 31:09.060
♪ Don't look back ♪

31:08.370 --> 31:09.440
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

31:09.470 --> 31:09.660
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

31:10.150 --> 31:11.890
♪ I've already learned ♪

31:10.170 --> 31:11.830
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

31:12.540 --> 31:16.440
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

31:17.110 --> 31:18.380
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

31:18.170 --> 31:18.900
[Cooperation Plan]

31:19.050 --> 31:21.670
[Return and Exchange Policy]
[Technical Support]

31:19.360 --> 31:23.550
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

31:24.500 --> 31:27.030
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

31:25.530 --> 31:26.510
You're so proactive.

31:26.510 --> 31:28.130
Aren't you afraid that he'll target you?

31:28.130 --> 31:30.390
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

31:28.380 --> 31:29.940
They can't fire me

31:29.960 --> 31:31.290
because I work hard, right?

31:31.290 --> 31:32.700
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

31:31.940 --> 31:32.760
And

31:32.780 --> 31:33.980
you said

31:34.060 --> 31:35.790
we must work together as a team.

31:53.260 --> 31:54.890
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

31:53.260 --> 31:55.630
We've contacted Yunhai Cotton Mill.

31:55.650 --> 31:57.370
The factory director will personally
lead the delivery team.

31:55.800 --> 31:57.800
[Reception Staff List for
Cotton Mill's Guests]

31:57.400 --> 32:00.130
They will arrive at
the hotel by 3 p.m. on the 17th.

32:00.350 --> 32:01.720
Why isn't Xu Miyu

32:01.720 --> 32:02.590
on the reception staff list?

32:02.590 --> 32:03.480
Because we arranged for leaders

32:03.480 --> 32:05.240
at the manager level and above

32:05.240 --> 32:06.480
to receive the VIPs.

32:06.500 --> 32:07.150
So...

32:07.200 --> 32:08.250
Add her to the list.

32:08.250 --> 32:09.320
She was the one
who made the connection with Yunhai.

32:09.320 --> 32:10.300
They won't accept anyone else.

32:10.300 --> 32:10.980
Yes, sir.

32:16.800 --> 32:17.730
Stand straight.

32:20.250 --> 32:21.330
Didn't I warn you

32:22.860 --> 32:26.120
that a wise man doesn't fight
when the odds are against him?

32:26.170 --> 32:28.330
Don't challenge Ji Feng.

32:29.100 --> 32:30.750
He's the Old Madam's favorite right now.

32:30.750 --> 32:31.850
He's not someone you want to mess with.

32:31.850 --> 32:33.240
Your top priority is to sort out

32:33.240 --> 32:34.920
the linen supply channel.

32:34.940 --> 32:36.940
Once we have real power,
we can take our time to plan.

32:36.940 --> 32:37.970
Haven't I said that?

32:37.970 --> 32:39.000
Zhigang,

32:39.550 --> 32:41.400
I did exactly what you wanted.

32:41.420 --> 32:42.550
It's Ji

32:43.310 --> 32:44.720
who picked on me.

32:46.480 --> 32:48.210
Look at this proposal you made.

32:48.620 --> 32:49.790
Everyone knows

32:49.790 --> 32:51.160
you took a kickback.

32:51.160 --> 32:53.590
I really didn't take much this time.

32:54.510 --> 32:55.980
Didn't take much?
Come here and read it.

32:55.980 --> 32:56.500
Take it.

32:57.800 --> 32:58.900
Look at their quotes.

32:58.900 --> 33:00.030
Then, look at yours.

33:00.220 --> 33:01.820
Why are you being so greedy?

33:02.290 --> 33:03.790
Who will want to work with you?

33:03.790 --> 33:04.930
Who would dare?

33:04.950 --> 33:05.950
You are so stupid.

33:09.120 --> 33:10.130
[Proposer: Xu Miyu]

33:10.760 --> 33:11.370
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

33:13.580 --> 33:14.260
I...

33:14.970 --> 33:16.610
I... I clearly...

33:16.640 --> 33:17.810
Shut up.

33:24.510 --> 33:28.360
[Yingfeng Logistics]

33:27.410 --> 33:28.160
Hello.

33:28.160 --> 33:29.550
Welcome! Welcome! Welcome!

33:29.550 --> 33:30.420
Hello!

33:30.440 --> 33:31.190
Welcome! Welcome!

33:31.190 --> 33:31.880
Hello!

33:31.910 --> 33:32.920
Thank you for your hard work.

33:32.920 --> 33:33.930
Hello.

33:34.270 --> 33:35.830
Come on, Ms. Xu, come here.

33:36.090 --> 33:37.040
Hello.

33:37.060 --> 33:37.480
Ma'am.

33:37.480 --> 33:38.270
Hello.

33:38.270 --> 33:38.880
Welcome.

33:38.880 --> 33:40.220
Thank you so much this time.

33:40.220 --> 33:40.920
Please come in.

33:40.920 --> 33:41.880
-Okay.
-Director.

33:41.880 --> 33:44.440
Director, sorry I didn't come out
to meet you.

33:44.880 --> 33:45.940
Welcome. Welcome.

33:46.120 --> 33:46.750
Hello. Hello.

33:46.750 --> 33:47.540
Welcome. Welcome.

33:47.540 --> 33:48.130
Hello. Hello.

33:48.130 --> 33:49.110
Hello. Hello.

33:49.330 --> 33:50.130
After you.

33:50.160 --> 33:50.840
Please.

33:50.880 --> 33:52.070
Okay. Okay. Okay.

33:52.350 --> 33:53.350
We must stand shoulder to shoulder

33:53.350 --> 33:54.830
for our cooperation.

35:06.250 --> 35:07.980
Wish our cooperation to go smoothly.

35:07.980 --> 35:09.640
That's what I hope for as well.

35:28.660 --> 35:30.000
Cooperating with Purong Hotel,

35:30.000 --> 35:31.850
a five-star hotel,

35:31.920 --> 35:33.550
is a stroke of luck for our factory.

35:33.550 --> 35:36.000
We've had more orders
than we can handle these days.

35:36.000 --> 35:38.070
You're too kind, Aslan.

35:38.070 --> 35:40.280
You helped Purong Hotel
go through this crisis.

35:40.280 --> 35:41.840
We are the ones who should thank you.

35:41.840 --> 35:43.070
Ms. Xu.

35:43.070 --> 35:44.880
Thank you so much for this.

35:44.880 --> 35:47.820
You are the benefactor of Yunhai.

35:47.840 --> 35:49.320
With such high-quality products,

35:49.320 --> 35:51.460
Yunhai should have been seen
by more people long ago.

35:51.460 --> 35:52.630
You flatter me.

35:52.630 --> 35:53.900
Thank you so much.

35:53.960 --> 35:54.640
Ms. Xu,

35:54.660 --> 35:55.710
meeting for the HSKP Department.

35:55.710 --> 35:57.110
Please reply if you copy.

35:57.450 --> 35:58.300
Copy that.

35:59.260 --> 36:00.960
The banquet is ready
in the Chinese restaurant.

36:00.960 --> 36:02.190
Someone will receive you there.

36:02.190 --> 36:03.360
Okay, go ahead with your work.

36:03.360 --> 36:03.710
Okay.

36:03.710 --> 36:04.840
I'll go now.

36:04.840 --> 36:05.370
Goodbye.

36:05.440 --> 36:06.000
Goodbye.

36:07.600 --> 36:09.780
[Purong Hotel and Yunhai Cotton Mill]

36:08.000 --> 36:09.510
Yin Xiang, time for the meeting.

36:09.510 --> 36:10.190
Coming.

36:09.800 --> 36:11.950
[Strategic Cooperation Signing Ceremony]

36:12.070 --> 36:13.480
Coming.

36:21.790 --> 36:23.690
I saw you in a video, look.

36:23.710 --> 36:25.440
The video of the contract signing
is posted.

36:25.440 --> 36:26.500
This is you, right?

36:26.700 --> 36:27.810
You're quite photogenic,

36:27.810 --> 36:28.930
even prettier than in person.

36:28.930 --> 36:29.780
Of course.

36:29.810 --> 36:30.990
You really know how to hide.

36:30.990 --> 36:33.050
Look how busy we've been all morning.

36:33.140 --> 36:35.160
And you went off to show off.

36:35.190 --> 36:37.620
It was required for work.

36:37.650 --> 36:39.780
Miyu needed a helper, so she called me.

36:40.740 --> 36:42.520
She is just a forewoman.

36:42.550 --> 36:44.050
Does she really think she's a boss?

36:44.050 --> 36:46.380
Relying on connections isn't real skill.

36:49.750 --> 36:50.500
Mr. Feng.

37:03.920 --> 37:05.390
Let's give a warm round of applause

37:05.390 --> 37:06.390
to welcome Mr. Ji.

37:10.890 --> 37:12.120
Okay, thank you.

37:24.760 --> 37:26.630
I want to share some good news.

37:27.110 --> 37:28.240
As of now,

37:28.370 --> 37:30.440
Purong Hotel has completed

37:30.460 --> 37:32.990
the replacement of linens
in all guest rooms.

37:33.070 --> 37:34.740
Thank you all for your full cooperation.

37:34.740 --> 37:35.450
Good job.

37:35.480 --> 37:36.080
Great.

37:42.670 --> 37:44.730
This was a very valuable experience.

37:45.220 --> 37:47.070
Rather than seeing it as a crisis,

37:47.070 --> 37:49.330
it's better to view it as an opportunity.

37:50.030 --> 37:52.500
We eliminated unqualified laundries,

37:52.530 --> 37:54.820
strengthened the management
of washing processes,

37:54.820 --> 37:58.280
and initiated cooperation
with a remarkable linen supplier.

37:58.530 --> 38:01.380
This is a breakthrough
for our HSKP Department.

38:03.120 --> 38:04.920
Our future will only get better.

38:05.030 --> 38:07.560
Please work together with me

38:07.730 --> 38:08.480
to move forward.

38:08.480 --> 38:09.110
Okay.

38:15.440 --> 38:17.510
And this time, the linen supply channel

38:17.510 --> 38:20.590
was spearheaded by
our executive floor forewoman, Xu Miyu,

38:20.590 --> 38:22.780
in cooperation with Yunhai.

38:22.910 --> 38:25.050
According to hotel management regulations,

38:25.050 --> 38:27.370
she should receive
the Outstanding Employee Award.

38:27.370 --> 38:29.930
The bonus will be issued
at the highest tier,

38:30.280 --> 38:31.340
ten thousand yuan.

38:31.370 --> 38:32.350
Oh my God.

38:32.440 --> 38:33.990
That could buy my life.

38:34.940 --> 38:36.620
In the future,

38:36.640 --> 38:39.210
any initiative taken
to share the hotel's burdens

38:39.210 --> 38:40.520
will be rewarded.

38:41.000 --> 38:43.140
This reward will not just be verbal,

38:43.710 --> 38:45.840
but will be reflected on your payroll.

38:46.380 --> 38:49.040
Conversely, any behavior detrimental
to the hotel's interests

38:49.040 --> 38:50.480
will not be tolerated.

38:50.900 --> 38:53.100
Anyone who slacks off at their post

38:53.130 --> 38:54.470
and just makes up the numbers

38:54.470 --> 38:56.320
will be punished accordingly.

38:56.870 --> 39:00.110
They will be demoted, receive pay cuts,
or even dismissed.

39:00.110 --> 39:02.110
Mr. Feng,

39:02.720 --> 39:04.920
do you have anything else to talk about?

39:05.050 --> 39:06.410
No, no.

39:07.320 --> 39:10.450
Good. We'll discuss the rest
at the directors' meeting.

39:11.180 --> 39:12.310
Meeting adjourned.

39:24.280 --> 39:25.920
[Transaction alert: Amount 10,000 yuan]

39:26.790 --> 39:28.190
I wish it were given to me.

39:39.860 --> 39:40.620
Okay.

39:42.850 --> 39:43.490
[Transaction in progress, please wait]

39:43.560 --> 39:45.250
[Preparing cash, please wait]

39:50.840 --> 39:53.510
We've all worked just as hard.

39:53.760 --> 39:54.840
Why did she just talk

39:54.840 --> 39:56.440
and get a 10,000-yuan bonus,

39:56.670 --> 39:58.590
while we don't even get overtime pay?

39:58.590 --> 40:00.480
She is Mr. Ji's favorite.

40:00.480 --> 40:01.280
If there are any perks,

40:01.280 --> 40:02.880
she'll definitely get them.

40:03.040 --> 40:05.320
How can we compare to her?

40:05.800 --> 40:07.880
We all did the work.

40:07.920 --> 40:09.800
But when it came to bonuses,
she took it all.

40:09.800 --> 40:10.440
Why?

40:10.440 --> 40:11.060
Exactly.

40:11.090 --> 40:12.770
Without us bottom-level workers,

40:12.770 --> 40:14.500
how could she claim any credit?

40:14.610 --> 40:15.610
Listen.

40:16.070 --> 40:18.190
We shouldn't listen to her anymore.

40:18.190 --> 40:20.440
We won't get any benefits
no matter how well we do anyway.

40:20.440 --> 40:22.440
Aren't you afraid she'll make things
difficult for you?

40:22.440 --> 40:24.150
If we all present a united front,

40:24.150 --> 40:26.080
she can't possibly wipe us all out.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.730
Why are you two so quiet?

40:31.550 --> 40:33.300
Don't drag me into your rebellion.

40:33.300 --> 40:33.990
Childish.

40:36.960 --> 40:38.030
Yin Xiang,

40:38.050 --> 40:40.140
aren't you going to suck up to her?

40:41.520 --> 40:43.030
Harmony brings wealth.

40:43.050 --> 40:44.690
Why make things so tense?

40:45.510 --> 40:46.400
Actually,

40:46.950 --> 40:47.960
Miyu isn't

40:47.960 --> 40:49.800
as difficult
to deal with as you think.

40:49.800 --> 40:51.520
She can be persuaded by reason
but not cowed by force.

40:51.520 --> 40:52.410
So,

40:52.430 --> 40:53.690
instead of going against her,

40:53.690 --> 40:55.070
it's better to just go along with her.

40:55.070 --> 40:57.570
Yes. She's quite nice,

40:57.600 --> 40:59.260
even a bit of a bleeding heart.

40:59.480 --> 41:01.200
We can just play the pity card with her.

41:01.200 --> 41:03.390
Just say, "Miyu, please,

41:03.440 --> 41:06.170
help me out, I can't do it."

41:06.230 --> 41:08.090
She'll immediately act like a cat

41:08.590 --> 41:09.990
which is sniffed catnip,

41:10.010 --> 41:11.300
getting all high.

41:11.410 --> 41:12.590
Then everything will

41:12.590 --> 41:14.320
just fall into place, won't it?

41:14.350 --> 41:15.960
We can take time off when we want,

41:15.960 --> 41:17.440
and slack off when we want.

41:17.460 --> 41:19.710
Anyway, she'll take care of
all the remaining work for you.
